      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
      "d335f602-a9c2-408a-ab5f-647170d22fbe"],
     " tableau weyl with the given content. The resulting standard Young \
tableaux form a basis spanning the Gelfand-Tsetlin subspace of the \
irreducible representation that is labeled by the ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      TemplateBox[{
        Cell[
         TextData["Weyl"]], "paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/ref/Weyl", 
        "QuantumMob Package Symbol"},
       "PackageLink",
