    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "GelfandClass[weyl, content] returns the standard Young tableaux in the \
Gelfand-Tsetlin class labeled by the Weyl tableau weyl with the given \
content. The resulting standard Young tableaux form a basis spanning the \
Gelfand-Tsetlin subspace of the irreducible representation that is labeled by \
the Weyl tableau weyl with the given content. This subspace is \
one-dimensional after applying the Young subgroup projector and is preserved \
by the chain of subgroups associated with content.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "GelfandClass", "titlemodifier" -> "", 
